5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"The Fabric Guide: Silk, Satin & Crêpe — What's the Difference and What's Right for You?\",\"description\":\"The complete guide to bridal fabrics. How to choose between silk, satin, crepe, and lace for your wedding dress.\",\"url\":\"https://juliekarn.com/blog/silk-wedding-dress-guide\",\"datePublished\":\"2025-02-15\",\"dateModified\":\"2025-03-01\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Julie Karn\",\"url\":\"https://juliekarn.com/about\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Julie Karn Bridal\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://juliekarn.com/logo.png\"}},\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580519542036-c47de6196ba5?w=1200&q=85&fit=crop\",\"inLanguage\":[\"he\",\"en\"],\"isPartOf\":{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"name\":\"Julie Karn Bridal\",\"url\":\"https://juliekarn.com\"}}"}}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://juliekarn.com\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://juliekarn.com/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"The Fabric Guide: Silk, Satin & Crêpe — What's the Difference and What's Right for You?\",\"item\":\"https://juliekarn.com/blog/silk-wedding-dress-guide\"}]}"}}],["$","$L10",null,{}],["$","$L11",null,{"post":{"slug":"silk-wedding-dress-guide","datePublished":"2025-02-15","dateModified":"2025-03-01","image":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580519542036-c47de6196ba5?w=1200&q=85&fit=crop","readingTime":5,"keywords":["silk wedding dress","שמלת כלה משי","satin wedding gown","wedding dress fabric guide","best fabric wedding dress","שמלת כלה סאטן"],"category":{"he":"חומרים","en":"Fabrics"},"title":{"he":"מדריך הבד: משי, סאטן וקרפ — מה ההבדל ומה נכון לך?","en":"The Fabric Guide: Silk, Satin & Crêpe — What's the Difference and What's Right for You?"},"description":{"he":"המדריך המלא לסוגי הבדים הנפוצים בשמלות כלה. איך בוחרים נכון בין משי, סאטן, קרפ ותחרה?","en":"The complete guide to bridal fabrics. How to choose between silk, satin, crepe, and lace for your wedding dress."},"content":{"en":[{"type":"p","text":"The single most impactful decision you will make about your wedding dress is not the silhouette or the neckline. It is the fabric. The same design in two different fabrics can look — and feel — like completely different dresses."},{"type":"h2","text":"Silk"},{"type":"p","text":"Pure silk is the benchmark against which all other bridal fabrics are measured. It drapes beautifully, photographs exceptionally well, and breathes in warm weather. The main types used in bridal design:"},{"type":"ul","items":["Silk charmeuse: ultra-fluid, lustrous, bias-cut heaven. Luxurious but unforgiving — requires a confident silhouette.","Silk crepe: structured, matte-finish, incredible drape. The fabric of choice for modern minimal dresses.","Silk georgette: sheer, light, layerable. Perfect for overlays, sleeves, and warm-weather gowns.","Silk organza: crisp, volume-friendly. Great for structured skirts and architectural shapes."]},{"type":"h2","text":"Satin"},{"type":"p","text":"Satin is defined by its weave structure, not its fibre content. It can be made from silk (the finest), viscose (a beautiful natural alternative), or polyester. What all satins share: a smooth, lustrous face and a matte back."},{"type":"ul","items":["Duchess satin: heavy, structured, the classic bridal satin. Holds its shape, photographs with beautiful light play.","Mikado: a silk-polyester blend, slightly crispy, beautiful for ballgowns and A-lines.","Viscose satin: excellent drape, more affordable than silk, great for minimalist gowns."]},{"type":"h2","text":"Crêpe"},{"type":"p","text":"Crêpe has emerged as one of the most popular bridal fabrics of the last decade — and for good reason. Its matte texture, slight stretch, and excellent drape make it universally flattering and easy to wear."},{"type":"p","text":"Silk crepe is the luxury choice. Polyester crepe can still be beautiful — but the quality varies significantly. Always ask to feel a swatch."},{"type":"h2","text":"Choosing your fabric: questions to ask"},{"type":"ul","items":["Indoor or outdoor ceremony? (Silk georgette in outdoor wind; duchess satin indoors)","Hot climate? (Lighter fabrics: georgette, crepe, chiffon)","Structured or fluid silhouette? (Structured: duchess satin, mikado; Fluid: crepe, charmeuse)","Photography style? (Matte crepe for editorial; shiny satin for classic glamour)"]},{"type":"cta","ctaText":"Discuss fabrics in a personal fitting →","ctaHref":"/book"}],"he":[{"type":"p","text":"ההחלטה שתשפיע הכי הרבה על שמלת הכלה שלך היא לא הגזרה ולא המחשוף. זה הבד. אותו עיצוב בשני בדים שונים יכול להיראות ולהרגיש כמו שמלות שונות לחלוטין."},{"type":"h2","text":"משי"},{"type":"p","text":"משי טהור הוא המידרש שכל שאר בדי הכלות נמדדים לפיו. הוא נופל יפה, מצולם מעולה ונושם בחום. סוגי המשי העיקריים בעיצוב כלות:"},{"type":"ul","items":["משי שרמז: זורם מאוד, מבריק, חתוך בייאס. מפנק אבל דורש בטחון בסילואט.","קרפ משי: מובנה, בגימור מט, נפילה מדהימה. בד הבחירה לשמלות מינימליסטיות מודרניות.","ג'ורג'ט משי: שקוף, קל, ניתן להשכבה. מושלם לשרוולים ושמלות לחום.","אורגנזה משי: נוקשה, ידידותי לנפח. נהדר לחצאיות מובנות."]},{"type":"h2","text":"סאטן"},{"type":"ul","items":["סאטן דאשס: כבד, מובנה, הסאטן הקלאסי לכלות. שומר צורה, מצולם עם משחק אור יפהפה.","מיקדו: שילוב משי-פוליאסטר, קצת קריספי, יפה לבולגאון ו-A-ליין.","סאטן ויסקוזה: נפילה מצוינת, יותר נגיש ממשי, נהדר לשמלות מינימליסטיות."]},{"type":"h2","text":"קרפ"},{"type":"p","text":"קרפ הפך לאחד מבדי הכלות הפופולריים ביותר בעשור האחרון — ובצדק. המרקם המט, המתיחה הקלה והנפילה המצוינת שלו הופכים אותו למחמיא לכולן ונוח ללבישה."},{"type":"cta","ctaText":"לדון בבדים בפגישה אישית ←","ctaHref":"/book"}]},"relatedLinks":[{"href":"/timeless-wedding-dresses","label":{"he":"שמלות כלה על-זמניות","en":"Timeless Wedding Dresses"}},{"href":"/dresses","label":{"he":"הקולקציה","en":"The Collection"}},{"href":"/blog/timeless-wedding-dress-guide","label":{"he":"מדריך שמלות על-זמניות","en":"Timeless Dress Guide"}}]}}],"$L12"]
